###Code and examples for the following courses in the Department of Computer Science
* [Data Structures (COMP 15)](https://github.com/tuftsdev/DataStructures)
* [Game Development (COMP 23 formerly COMP 50-GD)](http://tuftsdev.github.com/GameDevelopment/)
* [iOS for _Music Apps on the iPad_ course (COMP 150-ISW)](https://github.com/tuftsdev/ios)
* [Software Engineering (COMP 97 and 98 formerly COMP 180 and 190](http://tuftsdev.github.com/SoftwareEngineering/)
* [Web Programming (COMP 20)](https://github.com/tuftsdev/WebProgramming)
* [Web Engineering (COMP 120)](https://github.com/tuftsdev/WebEngineering)
